"Oh slag!"
She transformed into wolf mode and moved closer to the mysterious bot.
She growled loudly at it trying to draw it's attention off of 
Stringtra so she could get Quickstrike out of there. She flattened 
her ears back and arched her back.  She bared her teeth and continued 
to growl as loud as she could.
